 下载、打卡、拍照、公开课等，导致没有足够时间提升教学质量，关心学生心理成长变化。 蒋胜男指出，中小学教师是教育工作的中坚力量，他们所承受的行政压力直接关系到教育减负政策的实施效果。如果教师的行政压力无法得到缓解，教育减负政策将难以真正落地生根。这不仅会影响中小学教师的工作积极性和教学质量，还会将压力转嫁到广大学生及家长身上，对下一代的健康成长造成潜在威胁。 因此，建议采取切实有效的措施减轻中小学教师的行政压力，让他们能够专注于教书育人的本职工作。同时，坚决反对任何形式的转嫁压力行为，确保教育部门的工作不受外界干扰和压力的影响。（中国新闻周刊）"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-b8174a37efb97e37c446854573cd5497_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "36 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/646603701"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI9tTYrdXzqIQjEAMaCTEwNTk2NzMxNCD794WvBjAAOOECQBNyCTY0NjYwMzcwMXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "20_1709864650.385222", "card_id": "Q_647497393", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 197}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价《一人之下》漫画 662（703）话？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-42ad11362172236835443ff995e95dfc_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "36 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/647497393"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI9tTYrdXzqIQjEAMaCTEwNjE2NTYyOCCEyaevBjAAONcBQBRyCTY0NzQ5NzM5M3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "21_1709864650.385905", "card_id": "Q_646261970", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 38}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "人生到底需不需要「有目标」？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "还是走一步看一步？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-e2213c7add34d6b17f50c15aa61c4bb0_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "36 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/646261970"